Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: Prominent Plymouth Location - Direct ingress / egress to Highways 169 and 55, within 10 minutes of several affluent residential communities, over 830 covered and surface parking spaces, access in 173 miles of city, state and regional trails. From pond-side workspace and outdoor seating options to flexible interior floorplans, 505 and 605 Waterford offers the opportunity for large corporations and tight knit teams alike to join a growing office community.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Waterford Office Park is a two building (605 and 505), Class A united workplace campus prominently located in the heart of Plymouth off Highway 169 and Highway 55 with access to every necessity for a productive work day within the park.
